snippet.title: ConfEngine
snippet.description:
ConfEngine is the ultimate platform for managing conferences/events. 

We've released all the videos from the following conferences under creative commons license: 

* Agile India (https://agileindia.org)
* Open Data Science Conference (https://india.odsc.com)
* Selenium Conf (https://seleniumconf.in/)
* Appium Conf (https://appiumconf.com)
* Functional Conf (https://functionalconf.com/)
* jQuery Conf (https://jqueryconf.in/)
* Eclipse Summit (https://eclipsesummit.in/)
* Happiness at Work Conf (https://happinessconf.com/)
